is penans þat he sulde neuer whils he liffid̛ eatt garlykk̘ & he grawntid̛ þerto and went home so on̛ a tyme afterward̛ hym̛ happend̛ com̛ into a gartℏ þer garlykk̘ grew & he began̛ to hafe a liste to eatt þeroff and he durste not negℏ itt so on̛ a noder tyme he come vnto þe same gartℏ & he had sucℏ a luste vnto þis garlykk̘ þat he brakk his penance & tuke þeroff & ete it raw þat befor̛ he myght nowder ete raw nor soden̛ and belife page after hym̛ for * thoght itt & went vnto þe penytawnser & told̛ hym̛ & he with grete indignacion̛ putt hym̛ from̛ hym̛ & wold̛ enioyn̛ hym̛ no mor̛ penans bod reprovid̛ hym̛ cccl gula religiosos aliquando decipit cesarius tellis how som̛ tyme þer was a monk̘ of ceustus ordur and hym̛ happend̛ be made a bisshopp̛ and afterward̛ a cardinaƚƚ so on̛ a tyme hym̛ happend̛ to ride & emang aƚƚ þe felaship̛ þat was with hym̛ he spak vnto a monk̘ þat was bod lightlie letterd̛ & said̛ teƚƚ vs now som̛ gude wurd̛ or som̛ gude tale as we ride and he excusid̛ hym̛ faste & said̛ he cuthe nott & be no mene cuthe he gytt excusid̛ so at þe laste he began̛ att teƚƚ & said̛ vnto þis cardynaƚƚ when we shaƚƚ be dead̛ & broght into paradice þan̛ saƚƚ saynt benett com̛ & take vs in þat er cullid̛ with grete ioy & myrtℏ and þan̛ he saƚƚ speke vnto þe þat is a bisshop̛ & a cardynaƚƚ & say whatt erte þou and þou saƚƚ ansswer agayn̛ & say ffathur i am̛ a monke of ceustus ordur and he * nay þat erte þou nott ffor a monke is nott so gaylie arayed̛ as þou erte and þan̛ þou saƚƚ alege many thyngis for þe and þan̛ saƚƚ saynt benett giff a sentance & bid̛ þe porters oppyn̛ þi bodye & luke what at þai fynd̛ þerin and if ye fynd̛ þar cale & peas & benys & no noder meatt latt hym̛ com̛ in with þe monkis & if ye fynde þerin grete ffissℏ or delicatt meatis lat hym̛ stand þeroute what may þou þan̛ say þat now faris so wele and we far̛ so iƚƚ so þis cardinaƚƚ smylid̛ & commendid̛ hym̛ for his gude tale cccli gulosi in morte a demone degluciuntur saynt gregor̛ tellis of a mon